<L>__{interior london club night}
<C>__{earl of crabs}
<D>__{henri, this is mr. james cosgrove, who wishes to arrange a dinner party next week for sixty guests.}
<C>__{henri}
<D>__{i am at your service, mr. cosgrove. how much do you wish to spend?}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{as much as possible.}
<C>__{henri}
<D>__{as much as possible?}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{yes, for i wish to entertain splendidly.}
<C>__{henri}
<D>__{all the same, you must name an amount.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{it is entirely up to you. i want the best.}
<C>__{earl of crabs}
<D>__{may i suggest five hundred guineas?}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{will that be enough?}
<C>__{henri}
<D>__{last month, the duke of suffolk spent no more.}
<C>__{roderick}
<D>__{all right, five hundred guineas.}
